cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU to unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause NGU connection failure as the CU cannot establish GTP-U connection to the UPF.

du.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU to unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause NGU connection failure as the DU cannot establish GTP-U connection to the UPF.
du.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU 設定為無法到達的 IP '10.0.0.1' 會導致 NGU 連接失敗，因為 DU 無法與 UPF 建立 GTP-U 連接。
